cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this benchmark harness or its results in your work, please cite it."
title: "Gemma 4 Edge Benchmark: a reproducible vLLM evaluation harness for Gemma 4 26B-A4B on NVIDIA Jetson AGX Thor"
abstract: >-
  A reproducible benchmark harness that evaluates Gemma 4 26B-A4B served with
  vLLM on NVIDIA Jetson AGX Thor across grounded text, structured-output,
  multilingual, vision, tool-use, and systems workloads, with rubric-based
  semantic scoring and full request/response artifact capture.
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Ruan
    given-names: Jin Tan
repository-code: "https://github.com/ztanruan/gemma4-edge-benchmark"
url: "https://github.com/ztanruan/gemma4-edge-benchmark"
license: MIT
keywords:
  - gemma
  - vllm
  - jetson
  - edge-ai
  - llm-evaluation
  - benchmark
